<a href="/questions/1499985-why-did-the-main-character-want-to-go">Why did the main character want to go south? Was he suicidal? Why didn&#39;t he go north with his associates? How could they have filet mignons in a freezer when cows must have gone extinct at least a hundred years before??</a>
