<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Some study expedition about what was going on in the rest of the world, and searching for resources and other possible survivors. <br/>It was his job and s<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Some study expedition about what was going on in the rest of the world, and searching for resources and other possible survivors. <br />It was his job and someone had to do it. Different meat, I suppose? (Moose, caribou, seals are possibilities.). Or artificial meat.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
