        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer991493" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9228569591314943387">Dull plotting.<br/><br/>Duller psychology.<br/><br/>Shallow characters.<br/><br/>Improbable coincidences galore.<br/><br/>Pretty racist.<br/><br/>And yet almost entirely saved by some great descriptive work in painting the submerged world.<br/><br/>Worth reading, barely.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
